    "119625726": {
      "title": "A characteristic number of Hamiltonian bundles over S 2",
      "abstract": "Abstract Each loop ψ in the group Ham ( M ) of Hamiltonian diffeomorphisms of a symplectic manifold M determines a fibration E on S 2 , whose coupling class [V. Guillemin, L. Lerman, S. Sternberg, Symplectic Fibrations and Multiplicity Diagrams, Cambridge U.P., Cambridge, 1996] is denoted by c . If VTE is the vertical tangent bundle of E , we relate the characteristic number ∫ E c 1 ( VTE ) c n to the Maslov index of the linearized flow ψ t ∗ and the Chern class c 1 ( TM ) . We give the value of this characteristic number for loops of Hamiltonian symplectomorphisms of Hirzebruch surfaces."
    }
